Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:42.08,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,「人放弃生命的原因很多」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:48.29,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,「为了朋友 为了爱情 为了理想」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:54.19,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,「即使行刺也是出于同样的原因...」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:00:59.77,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,「在中国成为一个伟大的国家之前」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:01.67,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,「它共分为七个战国」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:09.27,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,「秦国暴君意欲扩充疆土」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:14.56,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,「停止战乱 一统天下」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:21.08,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,「他的理想正是建立在敌人的鲜血上」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:27.87,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,「因此任何战争都有双方的英雄...」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:42.57,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,「秦国」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:16.33,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I was orphaned at a young age and was
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:16.33,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我 自幼便为孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:19.82,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,never given a name. People simply called me "Nameless".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:19.82,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,也没有名字 人称“无名”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:22.40,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,With no family name to live up to, I devoted myself to the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:22.40,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,人若无名 便可专心练剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:23.84,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I spent 10 years perfecting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:23.84,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我花十年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:25.91,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,unique skills as a swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:25.91,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,练成一种独特剑法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.61,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The King of Qin has summoned me to court,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.61,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,秦王紧急召见我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:31.01,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,for what I have accomplished has
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:31.01,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是因为我已办成一件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:32.61,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,astonished the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:32.61,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,惊动秦国的大事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.93,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,「秦王宫殿」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.00,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,By order of his majesty,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:09.00,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣 奉我王之命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:12.33,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,we have traveled overnight to bring the warrior to see you, Prime Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:12.33,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,接壮士星夜兼程赶回 拜见承相
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:36.16,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Sky, Snow and Broken Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:36.16,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,长空 飞雪 残剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.85,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,For 10 years these three assassins from Zhao...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.85,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,这三名赵国刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:41.76,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,have repeatedly plotted to kill his majesty,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:41.76,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,十年来谋刺我王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:44.93,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,so he has not known a single peaceful night's sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:44.93,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,令我王一日不得安睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.03,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Today we discover that a hero from our great kingdom of Qin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.03,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,怎料今日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:52.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,has single-handedly wiped out the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:52.20,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,却被我大秦壮士一举击破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:56.97,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,From now on his majesty can once more sleep without fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:56.97,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,从此我王可以高枕无忧了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.18,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,His majesty's courtiers congratulate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.18,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣等恭贺我王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.01,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Heaven has sent a great warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.01,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,天降壮士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:04.05,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,to vanquish the assassins!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:04.05,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,剪除刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.77,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,By his majesty's command, summon the warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.77,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王令 召壮士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:05:00.77,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,When you enter the palace, always remain 100 paces from the throne...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:05:00.77,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,上殿拜见大王 需在百步之外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:05.02,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,or you will be killed without question. Please do not forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:05.02,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,否则格杀勿顶 壮士切记
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:38.60,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,For 10 years, no one's approached within 100 paces of the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:38.60,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,十年来 从未有人上殿近寡人百步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:39.87,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:39.87,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,可知为何?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.61,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Assassins were everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.61,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,刺客猖獗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:46.14,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Correct.As long as there are assassins, I cannot remove my armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:46.14,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,不错 刺客一日不除 我难解甲胄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.53,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Now that you have rooted out this evil on our behalf,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.53,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如今你替寡人除此大害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.92,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,what do you desire as a reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.92,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,要何封赏?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.59,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,To rid great Qin of its enemies is my duty. I desire no reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.59,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,为秦杀贼 不求封赏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.89,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,In accordance with Qin law, you must be properly rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.89,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大秦治下 必有封赏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:06.03,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Sky's silver spear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:06.03,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,长空银枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:11.40,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,has wounded untold numbers of our brave Qin warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:11.40,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,曾伤我大秦多少壮士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.14,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Pronounce my edict!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:14.14,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,宣我法令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:15.48,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,By order of his majesty, he who
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:15.48,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王法令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.42,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,vanquishes the assassin Sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.42,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,有破刺客长空者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.12,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,will be awarded 1,000 pieces of gold and authority over 1,000 households.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.12,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,赏千金 封千户侯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:24.60,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Advance within 20 paces of the throne and drink with his majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:24.60,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,上殿二十步 与王对饮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:43.03,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,According to my informants, you are a citizen of Qin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:43.03,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,据寡人接报 你是我秦国人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.81,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Your humble servant Nameless, Prefect of Lan Meng district.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.81,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣 狼孟县亭长无名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.85,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,A mere local Prefect! With authority over no more than 10 square miles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.85,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,区区亭长 辖区不过十里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:52.35,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,This is the lowest rank of office in our kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:52.35,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是我大秦国最小的官吏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:56.52,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What enabled you to overcome the three deadly assassins from Zhao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:56.52,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,有何本事 能破赵国的三大刺客?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.22,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I dealt with them one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.22,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,各个击破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.51,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Tell me in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.51,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,仔细讲来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:01.70,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Perhaps your majesty has heard that Broken Sword and Snow were lovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:01.70,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王可知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:04.40,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,残剑 飞雪为一对情侣?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.03,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Indeed I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.03,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.36,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,And was your majesty aware... that they had not spoken to each other for three years?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.36,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王可曾听说 他们三年无话?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.87,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Three years without words? Why was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.87,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,三年无话?为何?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:15.04,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Snow had spent one night with Sky as lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:15.04,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,皆因飞雪与长空曾有一夜之情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.85,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Broken Sword took this to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:17.85,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,使残剑耿耿于怀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:20.44,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Why have I not heard about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:20.44,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人怎么未曾听说呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:24.09,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,It took your servant much effort to uncover this secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:24.09,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣想方设法 才获此秘情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.95,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,To create a rift between Snow and Broken Sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.95,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,所以分化残剑飞雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:29.59,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I had first to dispose of Sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:29.59,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,必先取长空
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:34.05,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I am beginning to fathom your strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:34.05,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你的做法 寡人猜到一二了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:35.42,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Your majesty is most perceptive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:35.42,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王贤明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:38.26,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What did you use to defeat Sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:38.26,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,对长空 你以何为战?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:40.53,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:40.53,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.88,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Within Lan Meng it is my responsibility to arrest criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:45.88,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,在狼孟县 臣辎管缉捕盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.18,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,On the fifth day of the sixth month,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.18,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,六月初五
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.94,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Sky appeared in a chess house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.94,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,长空在一家棋馆内现身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:51.50,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I had heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.48,0:07:51.50,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣打听到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.38,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,that he was a lover of chess and  music, and was a frequent visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:54.38,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,他常来此地下棋听琴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.74,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The seven elite guards from Qin Court...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.74,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,秦宫七大高手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:19.30,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,We have been trailing you for days. You are under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.17,0:08:19.30,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,跟你多日 拿你归案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:23.17,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Reveal your weapon and identify yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.44,0:08:23.17,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,亮出银枪 验明正身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:02.06,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:02.06,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,慢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.67,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The local Prefect. What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.67,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,小小亭长 有何贵干?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.77,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,This region is under my control!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.77,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,此地归我辖管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.24,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.24,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.40,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You are a wanted criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.40,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你乃大王通缉的要犯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:21.17,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I am here to arrest you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:21.17,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我当拿你归案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:12:01.10,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Sir, would you be kind enough to play us another tune?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.54,0:12:01.10,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,老先生 请再抚一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.63,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Martial arts and music share the same principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:28.63,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,武功琴韵虽不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.37,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,but they share the same principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.37,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,但原理相通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.77,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Both wrestle with complex chords and rare melodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.77,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,都讲求大音希声之境界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:39.12,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,We stood facing each other for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:39.12,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣和长空面对面站着 有半个时辰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.25,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,neither of us made a move,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.25,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,虽然谁也没动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:44.67,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,while our combat unfolded
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:44.67,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,但决斗已经在彼此的意念中...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.08,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,in the depths of our minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.08,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,继续展开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.76,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,How swift your sword must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.76,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,好快的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:42.33,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I prided myself in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:42.33,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人自恃对秦国的一草一木...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:43.93,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,knowing every corner of our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:43.93,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:45.73,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Yet I was unaware that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:45.73,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,却不知狼孟县内
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:49.16,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,within the small district of Lan Meng there is such a talent like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:49.16,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,居然有你这样的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:55.47,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Broken Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.41,0:15:55.47,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,残剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.18,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Flying Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.18,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,飞雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:00.78,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,By edict of his majesty:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:00.78,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王法令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.78,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,the assassins Broken Sword and Flying Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.78,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,刺客残剑 刺客飞雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:05.55,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,have always worked as partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:05.55,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,素来联手行刺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:08.31,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,He who eliminates  either one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:08.31,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,有诛杀二人中任何一人者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:11.15,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,is awarded 10,000 pieces of gold and authority over 5,000 households.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:11.15,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,赏万金 封五千户侯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:12.45,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Advance within 10 paces and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:12.45,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,上殿十步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.23,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,drink with his majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:14.23,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,与王对饮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:25.76,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:25.76,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,三年前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:28.40,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Snow and Broken Sword stormed our palace together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:28.40,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,双剑联手攻入宫中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:32.13,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Three thousand soldiers were unable to resist them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.60,0:16:32.13,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,三千铁甲竟不能挡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:37.47,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I have since had this great hall emptied,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:37.47,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,从此寡人 将这大殿清扫一空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.61,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,so there is nowhere to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.61,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,使刺客无法藏身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.54,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that your sword was swifter than theirs combined?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:43.54,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你的剑竟能快过此二人?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:44.98,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.05,0:16:44.98,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.85,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,So how did you manage to overcome them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:49.85,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,那你如何取胜?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:16:59.69,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I was disguised as a citizen of Zhao and
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:16:59.69,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣乔装成赵人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:02.41,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,went searching for them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:02.41,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,去赵国寻找残剑飞雪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.90,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,It was rumored they were
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.90,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣探听到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.87,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,change their names and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.87,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,两人化名高山 流水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:10.01,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,hiding in a small calligraphy school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:10.01,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,藏身于赵国陉城一家书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:11.24,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I arrived as your
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:11.24,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,那天风闻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.35,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,majesty's troops approached.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.35,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王大军将要攻赵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:16.02,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,People fled in terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:16.02,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,陉城中百姓已逃散一空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.05,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Only the students and their master remained.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.05,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,只余下书馆弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:22.18,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Why have you come at such a time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:22.18,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,客人为何此时前来?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.79,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.79,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你是何人?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:26.89,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I am from a small province in Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:26.89,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,在下赵国易县人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:29.63,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,My father's dying wish was to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:29.63,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,先父临终留下遗愿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.53,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,acquire a scroll from your prestigious school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.53,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,求贵馆一副墨宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:35.29,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I fear this may be the last day of our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:35.29,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,今日 我书馆已是最后一日了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:41.11,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,- My honorable guest,whose calligraphy do you seek?  - Master Broken Sword's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:41.11,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,- 客人求何人之字?  - 求高山先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.64,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Broken Sword's power was immediately apparent to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:43.64,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,高山先生 便是残剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.78,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Rumor had it that his martial arts skills were rooted in his calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.78,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,传说他由书法中悟出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:50.71,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,In order to discover the swordsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:50.71,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,一套剑法 威力无比 臣对此颇有顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:53.69,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I had first to study the calligrapher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.72,0:17:53.69,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,所以臣想先看残剑的书法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:56.66,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Which character do you seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:56.66,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,求何字?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:57.89,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:57.89,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.29,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,My honored guest is fond of swords?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.29,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,客人是爱剑之人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:07.70,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I am merely fulfilling my father's last wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:07.70,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,在下只是完成先父的遗愿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:18.88,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What dimension of scroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:18.88,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,几尺?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.22,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Eight feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.22,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,八尺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.51,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,A scroll of that size requires red ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.51,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,八尺剑字 需要朱砂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:25.98,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Master wishes to borrow
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:25.98,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,有客人求字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:28.69,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,some red ink from the mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:28.69,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,主人特向小姐借朱砂一用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.99,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Master wishes to borrow some red ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.99,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,主人向小姐借朱砂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:44.47,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Has mistress heard my request?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:44.47,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,不知小姐听清了没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.25,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Master wishes to borrow some red ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.25,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,主人向小姐借朱砂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:51.77,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Tell him to come himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:51.77,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,叫他自己过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:08.67,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Your student respectfully requests some red ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:08.67,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,弟子来借朱砂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.65,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Broken Sword had not even started on the scroll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.65,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣求的“剑”字 还没有写成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.45,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,when your majesty's troops
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.45,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王攻赵的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:43.66,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,arrived at the city gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:43.66,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,此时已到陉城城外了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:32.12,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Prepare!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:32.12,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:53.84,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:53.84,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,射
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:59.21,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Your majesty's army has never lost a war...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:59.21,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王军队 之所以百战百胜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:00.78,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,because they never underestimate their  enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:00.78,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,除能征善战外
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:02.50,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Their tactics are brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:02.50,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,便在于弓强箭快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:06.75,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,and the archers are peerless in their range and accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:06.75,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,六国的箭都不及秦箭射得远
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:10.88,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Wherever they venture their
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:10.88,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王军队每到一处 必例行放箭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:13.49,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,reputation precedes them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:13.49,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,试探敌情 威慑四方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:28.84,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Storm! Storm! Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.90,0:21:28.84,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,风 风 风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:13.91,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You must all remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:13.91,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你们记住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.15,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,the arrows of Qin may be powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:17.15,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,秦国的箭再强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:20.72,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,They may penetrate our cities and destroy our kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:20.72,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,可以破我们的城 灭我们的国
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:23.89,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,But they can never annihilate our written words!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:23.89,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,可亡不了赵国的字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:26.62,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:26.62,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,今日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.93,0:22:30.99,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,you will all learn the true spirit of our art.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.93,0:22:30.99,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你们要学到赵国文字的精义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:01.53,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Storm! Storm! Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:01.53,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,风 风 风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.69,0:23:24.18,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The Zhao people, did they really not move?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.69,0:23:24.18,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,那些赵人 当真不动?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:26.32,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,People from Zhao are particularly strong in spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:26.32,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,赵国书法 刚烈过人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:29.25,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You asked for the character "Sword." Why was it difficult to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:29.25,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你所求“剑”字 有何难写?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:31.99,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,There are normally 19 ways of writing this character.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:31.99,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,“剑”字的写法 通常有一十九种
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:33.67,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What I requested from Broken Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:33.67,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣向残剑所求
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:36.70,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,was the 20th variation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:36.70,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是除去十九种变化的第二十种
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:38.07,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Calligraphy and swordplay...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:38.07,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,书法剑术
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.34,0:23:40.80,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,both rely on merging the power of the wrist... with the spirit in the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.34,0:23:40.80,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,都靠手腕之力与胸中之气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:42.03,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,This 20th variation would reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.97,0:23:42.03,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,这第二十种
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.34,0:23:45.21,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,the essence of his swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.34,0:23:45.21,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,便有他剑术的精妙藏于字中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:48.44,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,To think that one character can be written 19 different ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:48.44,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,一个字 竟有十九种写法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.27,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,How can people communicate when
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.27,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,又互不相认
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:52.01,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,they do not understand each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:52.01,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,极为不便
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.39,0:23:57.66,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Once I have conquered the six Kingdoms...and suppressed all other rebellious states,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.39,0:23:57.66,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,等寡人灭了六国之后 再灭其它诸国
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:24:00.29,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I shall rid the country of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.86,0:24:00.29,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,必将这些杂七杂八的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.49,0:24:01.65,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,these hopeless confusions,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.49,0:24:01.65,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,统统废掉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.86,0:24:05.29,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,keep one unified language for the whole land. Wouldn't that be something?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.86,0:24:05.29,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,只留一种 岂不痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.56,0:24:07.40,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Is your majesty not stopping after defeating the six Kingdoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.56,0:24:07.40,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王不是只灭六国吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.77,0:24:09.63,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The six Kingdoms are nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.77,0:24:09.63,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,六国算什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.87,0:24:12.36,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I intend to lead our army to every corner of this land...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.87,0:24:12.36,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人要率大秦的铁骑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.74,0:24:15.47,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,until we have established a vast and powerful empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.74,0:24:15.47,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,打下一个大大的疆土
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:20.61,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Storm! Storm! Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.81,0:24:20.61,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,风 风 风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.45,0:24:52.68,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You must be mistress Flying Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.45,0:24:52.68,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是流水先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.09,0:24:56.34,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,- Why are you leaving?  - I am going to fend off the arrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.09,0:24:56.34,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,- 为何离开?  - 我去挡箭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.76,0:24:58.59,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You are not needed. Please retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.76,0:24:58.59,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,不用你去 退下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.43,0:25:02.09,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The archers of Qin are legendary.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.43,0:25:02.09,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,秦军箭阵 闻名天下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.60,0:25:04.19,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Mistress Snow may not be able to repel them on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.60,0:25:04.19,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,流水先生未必能挡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.87,0:25:32.66,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Storm! Storm! Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.87,0:25:32.66,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,风 风 风
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.58,0:27:15.38,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You were quite brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.58,0:27:15.38,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,好身手
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.48,0:27:18.54,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Mistress Snow is far superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.48,0:27:18.54,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,流水先生更是好身手
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.15,0:27:20.45,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You have not come for the calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.15,0:27:20.45,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你不为求字而来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.39,0:27:23.25,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.39,0:27:23.25,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.76,0:27:25.49,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I have brought something
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.76,0:27:25.49,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,在下特地送一件东西
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.66,0:27:26.99,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.66,0:27:26.99,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,请先生过目
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.99,0:27:31.00,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Please meet me in the library at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.99,0:27:31.00,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,子夜 藏书阁
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.17,0:27:40.14,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Beautiful calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.17,0:27:40.14,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,好字
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.78,0:27:41.74,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Beautiful swordplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.78,0:27:41.74,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,好剑法
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.24,0:27:44.21,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,But you have not seen me use my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.24,0:27:44.21,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,先生并未看我出剑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.65,0:27:47.05,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Without your sword this scroll would not exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.65,0:27:47.05,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,若无你的剑 也无此字
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.62,0:27:49.64,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Please meet me in the library at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.62,0:27:49.64,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,今夜子时
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.05,0:27:52.92,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I have something to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.05,0:27:52.92,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,请先生去藏书阁看一件东西
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.96,0:27:55.42,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,While several hundred thousand Qin troops...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.96,0:27:55.42,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王几十万大军
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.69,0:28:00.23,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,were preparing for the next onslaught,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.69,0:28:00.23,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,当晚在山下安营扎寨准备攻赵
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.86,0:28:02.80,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I spent the night contemplating the scroll,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.86,0:28:02.80,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣则连夜悟字
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.06,0:28:05.56,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,hoping to discover the secret behind Broken Sword's skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.06,0:28:05.56,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,想找出残剑剑法之走势
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.35,0:28:19.47,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You say this calligraphy contains the mystery of swordplay,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.35,0:28:19.47,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你说这字中有剑法
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.68,0:28:23.24,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,but I cannot see anything unusual here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.68,0:28:23.24,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,可在寡人看来 这只是普通之字
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.79,0:28:27.52,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The brush and the sword are fundamentally connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.79,0:28:27.52,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,书法剑术 境界相通
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.89,0:28:29.52,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Their mystery is only revealed to those who can perceive the connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.89,0:28:29.52,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,奥妙全靠领悟
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.53,0:28:32.72,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,And you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.53,0:28:32.72,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你领悟到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.06,0:28:34.19,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Not entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.06,0:28:34.19,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,尚未悟透
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.66,0:28:38.29,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Then how were you able to challenge the two of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.66,0:28:38.29,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,悟不透 你如何挑战他们?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.55,0:28:51.54,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Sky fell by your sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.55,0:28:51.54,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,长空是败在你的剑下?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.11,0:28:53.01,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.11,0:28:53.01,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.55,0:28:58.75,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Why have you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.55,0:28:58.75,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你是何人?为何来此?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.25,0:29:00.55,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I am a citizen of Qin.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.25,0:29:00.55,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,在下实为秦人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.76,0:29:02.55,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I have a message from Sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.76,0:29:02.55,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,替长空带来一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.03,0:29:03.92,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.03,0:29:03.92,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,讲
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.29,0:29:05.23,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Sky said he had
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.29,0:29:05.23,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,长空说
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.43,0:29:08.12,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,always lived his life without burden or responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.43,0:29:08.12,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,他此生纵横江湖 无牵无挂
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.46,0:29:10.13,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Only one person had ever touched his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.46,0:29:10.13,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,唯有一人常留心中
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.63,0:29:12.43,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.63,0:29:12.43,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.87,0:29:13.89,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Flying Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.87,0:29:13.89,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,飞雪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.28,0:29:28.04,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Sky said he was certain Snow would avenge his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.28,0:29:28.04,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,长空说 飞雪定会替他报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.63,0:29:42.50,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,If you agree to a duel, meet me at the Qin army encampment tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.63,0:29:42.50,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,若要同在下一战 明日秦军大营
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.04,0:31:48.03,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.04,0:31:48.03,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你走
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.88,0:31:55.01,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.88,0:31:55.01,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.68,0:32:23.17,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I know you saw us!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.68,0:32:23.17,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道你看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.00,0:32:29.69,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I deliberately wanted you to see us!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.00,0:32:29.69,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我故意让你看见的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.67,0:32:34.43,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You are no longer in my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.67,0:32:34.43,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我心里根本没有你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.51,0:34:11.17,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,We are both very foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.51,0:34:11.17,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你我...都很蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.26,0:35:07.88,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I am not going to fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.26,0:35:07.88,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我不跟你动手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.99,0:35:09.86,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.99,0:35:09.86,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.67,0:35:16.30,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I am going to kill you and avenge my master!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.67,0:35:16.30,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我要杀了你 为主人报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.93,0:36:18.40,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Since you want to die, I shall assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.93,0:36:18.40,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你既然找死 我成全你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.54,0:38:43.92,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.54,0:38:43.92,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你笑什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.71,0:38:47.01,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What you did last night. It was unbelievably stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.71,0:38:47.01,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我笑你昨晚做了蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.06,0:39:30.65,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,When we fought,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.06,0:39:30.65,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,飞雪与臣决战时
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.90,0:39:32.92,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I could see that my plan had worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.90,0:39:32.92,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,因臣的计谋已然奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.30,0:39:36.03,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,She was emotional and agitated, unable to focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.30,0:39:36.03,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,所以她气血攻心 方寸大乱
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.40,0:39:38.46,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I defeated her easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.40,0:39:38.46,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣赢得丝毫不费力气
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.62,0:39:54.52,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Who would have thought that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.62,0:39:54.52,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,想不到残剑飞雪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.72,0:39:56.38,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Broken Sword and Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.72,0:39:56.38,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,竟如此怪异
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.59,0:39:58.42,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,were so emotionally fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.59,0:39:58.42,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,也会被情所困
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.38,0:40:19.87,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You are saying that you won by setting them against each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.38,0:40:19.87,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人听来 此战你赢在二人不和上?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.15,0:40:20.94,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.15,0:40:20.94,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.35,0:40:22.51,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,And the reason they became
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.35,0:40:22.51,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,之所以不和
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.71,0:40:25.65,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,enemies was because they were jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.71,0:40:25.65,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,二人必是心胸狭小之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.88,0:40:26.78,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.88,0:40:26.78,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.05,0:40:29.61,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Your story appears to make sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.05,0:40:29.61,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你讲的故事倒也合情合理
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.82,0:40:31.26,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,but in my opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.82,0:40:31.26,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,可寡人看来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.49,0:40:34.29,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,you have underestimated one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.49,0:40:34.29,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你把一个人想简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.59,0:40:36.39,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.59,0:40:36.39,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.43,0:40:38.26,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.43,0:40:38.26,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.26,0:40:42.72,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Would you like to know what kind of impression they made on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.26,0:40:42.72,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你想不想知 寡人对他们印象如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.47,0:40:46.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, I had once fought them face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.47,0:40:46.20,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,三年前 寡人曾与他们有过一战
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.17,0:40:48.70,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I found them
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.17,0:40:48.70,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,在寡人看来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.07,0:40:51.34,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,both honorable and exceptional,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.07,0:40:51.34,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,这二人光明磊落气度不凡
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.54,0:40:53.07,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,hardly the narrow-minded people you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.54,0:40:53.07,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,绝非小人之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.08,0:40:56.41,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,That is why Snow and Sky did not have an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.08,0:40:56.41,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 一夜之情是假
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.62,0:40:58.14,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Snow and Broken Sword were not enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.62,0:40:58.14,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,反目成仇是假
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.35,0:41:01.41,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,In other words,  your entire story is a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.35,0:41:01.41,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你所讲故事更是假
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.66,0:41:07.65,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Only one thing was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.66,0:41:07.65,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,只有一件事是真
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.29,0:41:12.82,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Sky must have known one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.29,0:41:12.82,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,长空认识你们其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.07,0:41:13.90,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.07,0:41:13.90,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.33,0:41:16.43,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.33,0:41:16.43,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.70,0:41:20.64,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I suspect you and Sky were allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.70,0:41:20.64,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人猜测你与长空早就相识
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.21,0:41:25.14,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You were able to defeat him for one reason only.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.21,0:41:25.14,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,长空败给你 只有一个理由
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.34,0:41:26.28,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.34,0:41:26.28,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,什么理由?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.05,0:41:29.60,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,He lost to you deliberately!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.05,0:41:29.60,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,故意求败
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.69,0:41:38.68,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,In order to assassinate me, the two of you staged a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.69,0:41:38.68,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你与长空为行刺寡人 暗自串通
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.89,0:41:41.62,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,using my guards as witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.89,0:41:41.62,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,引我秦宫高手在一旁观看作证
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.99,0:41:44.16,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Laying this trap was not difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.99,0:41:44.16,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,布此圈套 并不困难
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.40,0:41:46.46,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The hard part was in persuading Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.40,0:41:46.46,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,难在长空竟能将莫大信任
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.67,0:41:47.93,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,to place his life in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.67,0:41:47.93,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,托付给你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.83,0:41:51.93,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Your sword may be swift, but not enough to defeat Sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.83,0:41:51.93,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你的剑虽快 未必能胜得了长空
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.27,0:41:54.93,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Yet he willingly fell under your blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.27,0:41:54.93,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,但长空却自愿倒在你的剑下
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.31,0:41:57.47,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What courage, what gallantry!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.31,0:41:57.47,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如此胸怀 令人叹服
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.01,0:41:59.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,So Sky became
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.01,0:41:59.20,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,所以长空是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.41,0:42:01.31,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,your first accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.41,0:42:01.31,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,第一位捐助者
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.82,0:42:06.31,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Sky was a proud man,who regarded himself without
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.82,0:42:06.31,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人在想 长空心高气傲
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.52,0:42:08.18,英文字幕,,0,0,0,, equal in this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.52,0:42:08.18,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,自认天下无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.42,0:42:10.98,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What made him think that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.42,0:42:10.98,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,他何以认定 他做不到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.19,0:42:12.66,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,you would succeed where he had failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.19,0:42:12.66,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,唯你能成功?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.36,0:42:17.76,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Unless, in order to assassinate me,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.36,0:42:17.76,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,莫非你专为行刺而十年练剑?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.10,0:42:20.51,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,you had spent the last 10 years honing a unique skill,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.10,0:42:20.51,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你的剑术中藏有一式
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.70,0:42:23.19,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,a lethal maneuver that no one can counter?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.70,0:42:23.19,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,威力巨大 无人能比?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.68,0:42:37.14,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Having defeated Sky, you could already come within 20 paces of the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.68,0:42:37.14,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,得到长空 你已能上殿二十步
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.42,0:42:39.94,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Why did you need Broken Sword and Snow as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.42,0:42:39.94,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,为何还寻找残剑 飞雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.55,0:42:43.32,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I suspect you have to be within 10 paces of your target to be effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.55,0:42:43.32,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人猜想 你所练行刺剑法
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.66,0:42:45.52,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,一定以十步为距
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.59,0:42:49.79,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,So, you required
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.59,0:42:49.79,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 你还需利用寡人的悬赏令
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.00,0:42:51.69,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,one more accomplice to help you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.00,0:42:51.69,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寻找第二名捐助者
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.90,0:42:53.23,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,advance another 10 paces!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.90,0:42:53.23,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,再进十步
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.93,0:42:57.63,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I believe that even though Broken Sword and Snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.93,0:42:57.63,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人以为 残剑飞雪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.84,0:42:59.92,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,had never met Sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.84,0:42:59.92,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,虽与长空素昧平生
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.04,0:43:00.97,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,They understood at once
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.04,0:43:00.97,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,但立即明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.17,0:43:03.70,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,why he had agreed to your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.17,0:43:03.70,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,长空故意求败的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.89,0:43:18.91,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,How far am I from the bookshelves?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.89,0:43:18.91,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,此处距书简几步?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.49,0:43:21.62,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,About 10 paces..
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.49,0:43:21.62,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大约十步
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.06,0:43:23.86,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Good. Ten paces it is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.06,0:43:23.86,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,好 就是十步
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.37,0:44:10.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I only need one of you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.37,0:44:10.20,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,在下只需一人相助
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.58,0:44:12.04,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Please decide between yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.58,0:44:12.04,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,两位请自行决定
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.41,0:44:13.88,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning, at the Qin army encampment.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.41,0:44:13.88,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,明晨 秦军大营
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.76,0:44:28.82,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,How swift his sword is!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.76,0:44:28.82,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,好快的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.93,0:44:31.79,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.93,0:44:31.79,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.23,0:44:33.63,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Sky was one of the greatest warriors of our times.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.23,0:44:33.63,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,长空是当今大侠
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.77,0:44:36.76,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Yet he was willing to give his life to this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.77,0:44:36.76,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,竟能将性命交与此人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.17,0:44:39.66,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,That is why he has the ability to assassinate Qin's king.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.17,0:44:39.66,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,所以他能够刺秦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.34,0:44:45.40,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,We must go tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.34,0:44:45.40,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我们要去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.34,0:44:49.25,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,To go is to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.34,0:44:49.25,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,去 就是死
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.18,0:44:53.62,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Then let us die together.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.18,0:44:53.62,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,死就一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.39,0:45:57.35,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You are one step ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.39,0:45:57.35,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我比你晚了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.45,0:46:20.01,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I fear I have inflicted too deep a wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.45,0:46:20.01,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我怕把你伤得太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.62,0:46:22.85,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I should have been the one to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.62,0:46:22.85,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,应该是我去
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.56,0:46:27.05,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I want you to go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.56,0:46:27.05,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我要你活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.76,0:46:30.96,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,If you died, how could I live?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.76,0:46:30.96,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你死了 我怎么活?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.07,0:46:37.06,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Promise me you will live well when I have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.07,0:46:37.06,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你答应我 要好好的活
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.31,0:46:46.34,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.31,0:46:46.34,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.53,0:46:59.52,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.53,0:46:59.52,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.01,0:47:10.34,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Moon will soon be here to take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.01,0:47:10.34,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如月快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.64,0:47:15.63,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.64,0:47:15.63,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.81,0:48:50.52,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Your servant Nameless, the Prefect of Lan Meng.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.81,0:48:50.52,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,在下狼孟县亭长无名
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.82,0:48:53.99,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I have come to Zhao to catch this assassin. Please let me fight her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.82,0:48:53.99,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,捉拿赵国刺客到此 肯请单独一战
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.59,0:48:56.65,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,This is a dangerous criminal wanted by his majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.59,0:48:56.65,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,此人是大王通缉的要犯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.86,0:48:59.48,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Now that she has been found, it is my duty to arrest her.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.86,0:48:59.48,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,既在此地现身 我当就地擒拿
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.89,0:49:01.92,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I have a prior agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.89,0:49:01.92,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,在下与刺客曾有言在先
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.26,0:49:03.75,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,with the assassin to fight her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.26,0:49:03.75,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,要单独决一胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.10,0:49:05.12,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,If I am unable to succeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.10,0:49:05.12,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如在下不能取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.43,0:49:07.42,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,please feel free to step in.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.43,0:49:07.42,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,再有劳将军援手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.97,0:49:09.09,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Please grant me permission to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.97,0:49:09.09,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,望将军恩准
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.52,0:49:52.42,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Unsheathe your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.52,0:49:52.42,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,出你的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.15,0:50:26.05,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Storm! Storm! Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.15,0:50:26.05,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,风 风 风
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.71,0:50:27.54,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Make your move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.71,0:50:27.54,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,快动手
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.58,0:50:30.94,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Storm! Storm! Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.58,0:50:30.94,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,风 风 风
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.01,0:50:34.68,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I die willingly for our cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.01,0:50:34.68,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,为刺秦我死而无憾
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.92,0:50:35.68,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Please make your move!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.92,0:50:35.68,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,请动手吧
