Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.10,0:51:18.70,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大风 大风 大风
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.42,0:51:36.45,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,How swift your sword is!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.42,0:51:36.45,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,好快的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.50,0:52:41.23,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I suspect you had a battle
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.50,0:52:41.23,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人猜测 你与残剑之间
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.43,0:52:42.87,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,with Broken Sword as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.43,0:52:42.87,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,也曾有一战
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.03,0:52:44.07,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Like the fight between you and Sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.03,0:52:44.07,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,跟长空一样
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.44,0:52:45.78,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,you and Broken Sword fought
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.44,0:52:45.78,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你们二人的交手
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.08,0:52:48.38,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,in the depth of your minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.08,0:52:48.38,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,也是在意念中完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.81,0:52:51.40,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Except neither of you wanted to harm the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.81,0:52:51.40,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,但此次 绝非生死之战
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.56,0:52:55.73,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,but were content to go through the honorable motions.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.56,0:52:55.73,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,而是在想像中 轻轻点到为止
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.91,0:52:58.87,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,This was also a tribute to Snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.91,0:52:58.87,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如此 也是为了祭奠飞雪
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.99,0:56:07.26,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Master asked me to give you his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.99,0:56:07.26,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,主人交你此剑
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.50,0:56:13.52,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Why has he done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.50,0:56:13.52,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,为何交剑?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.24,0:56:16.36,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Master and Snow will always be together in life or in death,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.24,0:56:16.36,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,残剑飞雪 生死相守
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.67,0:56:20.94,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,and their swords will never be apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.67,0:56:20.94,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,人不离人 剑不离剑
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.85,0:56:33.29,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Master asked me to give you his sword
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.85,0:56:33.29,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,主人给你此剑
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.62,0:56:34.88,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,to help assassinate Qin's king.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.62,0:56:34.88,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,助你一同刺秦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.56,0:57:09.25,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Sky, Broken Sword and Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.56,0:57:09.25,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,长空 飞雪 残剑
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.46,0:57:11.76,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,gave themselves in different ways,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.46,0:57:11.76,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,分别以不同方式捐出自己
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.03,0:57:14.50,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,in order that you could come within 10 paces of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.03,0:57:14.50,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,助你上殿十步来刺寡人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.70,0:57:17.40,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,All three were willing to entrust their lives to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.70,0:57:17.40,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,此三人能把生命托付给你
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.60,0:57:20.44,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Surely one can ask no more of a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.60,0:57:20.44,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,人生知己 也莫过于此了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.01,0:57:22.37,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,That is why you are
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.01,0:57:22.37,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.57,0:57:24.01,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,the most dangerous assassin of them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.57,0:57:24.01,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,最危险的刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.39,0:57:38.91,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,How did your majesty figure this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.39,0:57:38.91,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王何以识破?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.29,0:57:41.26,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The candle flames in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.29,0:57:41.26,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人面前的烛火...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.66,0:57:44.53,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,can sense your murderous intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.66,0:57:44.53,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,感到了你的杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.27,0:57:53.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The three of them, and you,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.27,0:57:53.20,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,他们三人 还有你...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.97,0:57:55.56,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,were all willing to die for your cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.97,0:57:55.56,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,舍身取义
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.41,0:57:59.50,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I am ashamed to say I cannot measure up to your courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.41,0:57:59.50,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人自愧不如
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.85,0:58:01.71,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Your majesty has seen through our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.85,0:58:01.71,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王毕竟识破了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.02,0:58:06.68,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I have only just worked it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.02,0:58:06.68,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人也是刚刚识破
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.35,0:58:11.19,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Why else would I have allowed you to come this close?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.35,0:58:11.19,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,否则 怎会容你近我十步
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.36,0:58:14.76,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,A man from Qin would never try to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.36,0:58:14.76,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,秦人不会刺我
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.96,0:58:16.29,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.96,0:58:16.29,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你到底是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.50,0:58:17.83,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I am a man of Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.50,0:58:17.83,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣实为赵人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.60,0:58:21.86,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,My family was killed by the Qin army.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.60,0:58:21.86,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣家人被秦军所杀
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.07,0:58:23.47,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Orphaned, I was taken in
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.07,0:58:23.47,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,自幼流落在秦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.67,0:58:25.03,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,by a family here in Qin.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.67,0:58:25.03,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,被秦人收养
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.24,0:58:27.00,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago I discovered my real identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.24,0:58:27.00,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,十年前知道身世
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.47,0:58:29.06,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,and decided to assassinate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.47,0:58:29.06,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,便决心行刺
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.81,0:58:31.50,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,So you are here on behalf of Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.81,0:58:31.50,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,为赵而来
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.55,0:58:36.38,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.55,0:58:36.38,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.28,0:58:38.61,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I presume you have
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.28,0:58:38.61,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.28,0:58:41.18,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,perfected a lethal move?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.28,0:58:41.18,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你练的快剑名称
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.45,0:58:42.68,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Just as your majesty suggests,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.45,0:58:42.68,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如大王所猜
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.16,0:58:44.42,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,there is indeed such a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.16,0:58:44.42,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,藏有一式
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.89,0:58:45.82,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,And what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.89,0:58:45.82,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,哪一式?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.39,0:58:47.72,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Within 10 paces I cannot fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.39,0:58:47.72,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,十步一杀
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.23,0:58:51.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Within 10 paces? I congratulate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.23,0:58:51.20,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,十步一杀?好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.00,0:58:53.19,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,My guards are outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.00,0:58:53.19,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人的卫士
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.40,0:58:55.46,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,100 paces away,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.40,0:58:55.46,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,均在殿外的百步之遥
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.67,0:58:57.90,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,while you are only 10 paces from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.67,0:58:57.90,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,而你近寡人已十步
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.97,0:59:00.03,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,It would seem that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.97,0:59:00.03,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,看来...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.64,0:59:04.23,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I shall not escape my fate today.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.64,0:59:04.23,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人今日是难逃此劫
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.65,0:59:13.52,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,And yet you hesitate?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.65,0:59:13.52,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你的杀气在乱?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.82,0:59:16.41,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Your majesty is most perceptive.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.82,0:59:16.41,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王见识过人
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.22,0:59:18.21,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.22,0:59:18.21,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.39,0:59:21.66,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,you have also underestimated somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.39,0:59:21.66,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王也把一个人想简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.86,0:59:23.69,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.86,0:59:23.69,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.96,0:59:24.99,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Broken Sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.96,0:59:24.99,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,残剑
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.50,0:59:34.03,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,It was imperative  that I proved to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.50,0:59:34.03,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣要向他们证明
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.27,0:59:37.67,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,that my sword was not only swift, but perfectly accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.27,0:59:37.67,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣的剑不仅快 且精准无误
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.79,1:00:24.22,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Within 10 paces I can strike
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.79,1:00:24.22,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,在下所练快剑
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.42,1:00:26.22,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,with surgical precision.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.42,1:00:26.22,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,十步之内 绝无偏差
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.63,1:00:28.72,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The sword will enter and exit the body avoiding all vital organs,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.63,1:00:28.72,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,若从膈腧穴入 步廊穴出
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.93,1:00:32.14,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,so the wound is deep but not fatal.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.93,1:00:32.14,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,便能不伤脏器 令人伤而不死
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.77,1:00:34.36,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I respectfully request one of you to take such a blow from me...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.77,1:00:34.36,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,只求两位中任何一位
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.90,1:00:38.23,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,in order to deceive Qin's king.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.90,1:00:38.23,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,能当众受我一剑 骗过秦王耳目
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.54,1:00:43.30,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,To take such a blow from you asks a great deal of us.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.54,1:00:43.30,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,当众受你一剑 岂是儿戏
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.94,1:00:45.34,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,How is Sky now?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.94,1:00:45.34,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,长空现在如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.78,1:00:46.87,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Almost fully recovered.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.78,1:00:46.87,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,现已无妨
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.35,1:00:49.58,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,He certainly had faith in your skills.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.35,1:00:49.58,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,难得他对你的剑法如此信任
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.98,1:00:52.18,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The security around the king is impenetrable.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.98,1:00:52.18,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,秦王防范严密 无法接近
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.82,1:00:54.01,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,This is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.82,1:00:54.01,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,只能如此
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.29,1:00:56.92,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The imperial guards are not worth a mention.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.29,1:00:56.92,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,那些秦宫卫士 不值一提
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.89,1:01:00.76,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The King of Qin should have died three years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.89,1:01:00.76,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,其实三年前 秦王就该死了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.03,1:01:02.02,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.03,1:01:02.02,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,何以失手?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.06,1:01:06.40,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I did not go through with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.06,1:01:06.40,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是我放弃了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.87,1:01:13.17,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The King of Qin must not be killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.87,1:01:13.17,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,秦王不能杀
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.67,1:01:15.04,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Broken Sword said that?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.67,1:01:15.04,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,残剑这样讲?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.28,1:01:15.90,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.28,1:01:15.90,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.11,1:01:17.01,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.11,1:01:17.01,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,为何?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.24,1:01:18.44,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I asked the same question.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.24,1:01:18.44,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣也这样问他
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.01,1:01:20.00,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What was his answer?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.01,1:01:20.00,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,他如何作答?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.38,1:01:22.28,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,He was unwilling to explain on that day.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.38,1:01:22.28,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,当日残剑不愿细说
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.35,1:01:26.41,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Sky, Snow, Broken Sword.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.35,1:01:26.41,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,长空 飞雪 残剑
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.69,1:01:28.92,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Of the three, only Broken Sword
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.69,1:01:28.92,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,三人中唯有残剑的剑法
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.08,1:01:30.65,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,was my match.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.08,1:01:30.65,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,与臣不相上下
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.56,1:01:36.15,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,That was why... what he said next...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.56,1:01:36.15,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,因此 残剑后来对臣说的话
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.90,1:01:38.83,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,worried me greatly.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.90,1:01:38.83,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,使臣颇有顾虑
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.50,1:01:40.52,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,As long as I am alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.50,1:01:40.52,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,有我在
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.80,1:01:42.29,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I shall prevent you from assassinating the king.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.80,1:01:42.29,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,便要阻止你刺秦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.77,1:01:47.00,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I am willing to help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.77,1:01:47.00,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我愿助你
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.58,1:01:52.60,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, somebody wasted a golden opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.58,1:01:52.60,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,三年前 有人错失良机
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.68,1:01:55.67,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,This time, we must not fail.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.68,1:01:55.67,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,这次 一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.72,1:01:58.48,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning, I shall meet you at the Qin encampment.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.72,1:01:58.48,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,明早 秦军大营见
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.56,1:02:06.75,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I would like to ask a favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.56,1:02:06.75,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你帮我一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.33,1:02:09.19,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Help me to fight him now.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.33,1:02:09.19,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,出剑助我
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.27,1:02:21.97,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.27,1:02:21.97,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.92,1:02:29.88,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.92,1:02:29.88,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,还不出剑?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.75,1:02:34.05,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Although I had agreed to help Snow,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.75,1:02:34.05,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,臣虽答应飞雪出剑相助
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.85,1:02:37.12,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,it did not seem honorable to attack Broken Sword.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.85,1:02:37.12,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,但总以为有失正大光明
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.36,1:02:38.88,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I found myself unable to make a move,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.36,1:02:38.88,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,故迟迟不能出手
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.89,1:02:41.62,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,although we both knew that...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.89,1:02:41.62,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,然而臣与飞雪都明白
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.30,1:02:43.59,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,if we did not stop Broken Sword,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.30,1:02:43.59,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如不阻挡残剑
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.36,1:02:45.89,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,we would have no chance of success.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.36,1:02:45.89,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,便绝无成功可能
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.48,1:04:36.50,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Moon, stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.48,1:04:36.50,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如月住手
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.05,1:04:40.64,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You are no match for him! Let it go!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.05,1:04:40.64,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你不是他对手 住手吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.24,1:05:06.64,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I knew you would do this.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.24,1:05:06.64,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道你会这样做
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.64,1:05:10.27,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Now you cannot stand in my way.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.64,1:05:10.27,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,这样你就不能拦我了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.68,1:05:13.38,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Even wounded I can still stop you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.68,1:05:13.38,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,就算伤我 我还会阻拦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.42,1:05:16.68,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,In that case I shall have to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.42,1:05:16.68,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,那我会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.33,1:05:25.16,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I worry I may have wounded him too deeply.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.33,1:05:25.16,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我怕把他伤得太重了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.35,1:05:30.42,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,With mistress' medicine Master should be out of danger in a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.35,1:05:30.42,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,有小姐的创伤药 一日后 应无大碍
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.50,1:05:32.63,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Have you delivered the medicine yet?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.50,1:05:32.63,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,药送了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.17,1:05:35.66,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I tended Master's wound myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.17,1:05:35.66,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是我亲手替先生敷上的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.47,1:05:39.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,After the duel today, take my sword
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.47,1:05:39.20,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,今天战后 你捧飞雪剑
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.41,1:05:41.37,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,and follow the Qin army into court.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.41,1:05:41.37,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,跟来人进秦宫
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.38,1:05:44.79,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,- I will.  - The Qin guards will not ill-treat a servant.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.38,1:05:44.79,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,- 是  - 秦国不会为难你这个下人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.05,1:05:47.38,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,If the assassination is successful,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.05,1:05:47.38,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如刺秦成功
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.39,1:05:49.72,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,return with a red flag.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.39,1:05:49.72,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,打红旗回来
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.42,1:05:52.68,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,If it fails, a yellow one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.42,1:05:52.68,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,失败了 黄旗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.09,1:05:55.32,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,If mistress meets with misfortune at the duel,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.09,1:05:55.32,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,小姐 此战若有不幸
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.53,1:05:56.86,英文字幕,,0,0,0,, what would be the point?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.53,1:05:56.86,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,报信何用?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.23,1:06:01.72,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,When I look down from heaven,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.23,1:06:01.72,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,那我在天之灵
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.30,1:06:03.99,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,the red flag will bring a smile to my lips.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.30,1:06:03.99,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,见红旗也会含笑
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.10,1:06:55.12,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,How is Snow?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.10,1:06:55.12,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,飞雪如何?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.60,1:06:56.79,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,She is recovering.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.60,1:06:56.79,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,正在养息
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.44,1:07:02.84,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I am here without her knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.44,1:07:02.84,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我是背着她而来
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.07,1:07:05.94,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You once said as long as you are here you would try to stop me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.07,1:07:05.94,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你曾说过 有你在便会阻挡
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.34,1:07:07.94,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Abandon your plan to assassinate the king.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.34,1:07:07.94,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,请你放弃刺秦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.28,1:07:09.68,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Do you know I am from Zhao?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.28,1:07:09.68,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你可知我是赵人?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.95,1:07:10.92,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,So am I.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.95,1:07:10.92,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.38,1:07:12.82,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Does Qin intend to destroy Zhao?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.38,1:07:12.82,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,秦国是否要灭赵?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.38,1:07:14.28,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.38,1:07:14.28,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.52,1:07:16.32,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Is the King of Qin an enemy of Zhao?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.52,1:07:16.32,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,秦王是否赵国的敌人?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.62,1:07:17.49,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.62,1:07:17.49,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.46,1:07:19.75,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Then whom do you speak for?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.46,1:07:19.75,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,那你在替谁说话?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.16,1:07:21.39,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,How can you call yourself a man of Zhao?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.16,1:07:21.39,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你如何配做赵人?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.76,1:07:29.72,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Snow asked me the same question once.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.76,1:07:29.72,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你的话 飞雪也曾经这样问我
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.87,1:07:34.34,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The year we met I was a wanderer
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.87,1:07:34.34,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,那年 我浪迹江湖
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.07,1:07:37.14,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,with no home to call my own.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.07,1:07:37.14,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,碰到飞雪
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.52,1:07:41.78,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,She was the daughter of the great general Zhao Zhen,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.52,1:07:41.78,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,飞雪是赵国大将赵震之女
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.49,1:07:44.75,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,who lost his life during a battle against Qin.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.49,1:07:44.75,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,秦赵之战中 赵震身亡
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.16,1:07:46.59,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Snow inherited his sword.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.16,1:07:46.59,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,传下飞雪剑给她
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.86,1:07:49.49,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,She had vowed to avenge her father's death.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.86,1:07:49.49,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道飞雪立志刺秦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.86,1:07:52.52,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I wanted to help her.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.86,1:07:52.52,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,为父报仇 便有心帮她
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.97,1:07:57.03,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Calligraphy and swordplay share the same source and principles.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.97,1:07:57.03,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,书法剑术 同源同理
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.87,1:07:59.43,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,So we practiced calligraphy every day,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.87,1:07:59.43,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我和飞雪每日习字
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.94,1:08:02.13,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,in the hope that it would refine our skills,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.94,1:08:02.13,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,想从书法中悟出一套剑法
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.47,1:08:03.46,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,and increase our power.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.47,1:08:03.46,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,增进功力
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.81,1:08:08.71,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Snow knew I had been rootless since childhood,living nowhere and everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.81,1:08:08.71,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,飞雪知道 我从小浪迹江湖 四海为家
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.51,1:08:12.77,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,She often said to me, once we had succeeded in killing the king,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.51,1:08:12.77,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,便常对我说 等完成刺秦心愿
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.97,1:08:14.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,she would take me back to her home.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.97,1:08:14.20,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,就带我回她的家
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.88,1:08:18.94,英文字幕,,0,0,0,, She said no swords existed there, and no swordsmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.88,1:08:18.94,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,她说 那里没有剑 也没有剑客
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.09,1:08:20.22,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,There would only be a man
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.09,1:08:20.22,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,只有一个男人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.43,1:08:21.41,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,and a woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.43,1:08:21.41,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,和一个女人
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.59,1:08:44.78,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The truth of calligraphy has to be intuitively grasped.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.59,1:08:44.78,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,书法之真谛 在于意境
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.36,1:08:46.48,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,It is the same with swordplay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.36,1:08:46.48,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,剑法也如此
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.29,1:08:49.32,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Both seek to return to a state of simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.29,1:08:49.32,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,讲求返璞归真之境界
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.93,1:08:52.12,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Gradually I began to understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.93,1:08:52.12,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,于是 我慢慢领悟了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.17,1:09:01.16,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, I reached the peak of my training.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.17,1:09:01.16,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,三年前 剑法练成
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.64,1:09:03.34,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Snow felt it was time to attempt the assassination.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.64,1:09:03.34,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,飞雪执意要去刺秦
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.94,1:09:06.28,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Together we stormed the palace.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.94,1:09:06.28,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我便随飞雪一同杀入秦宫
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.19,1:13:11.06,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Snow asked me why did I not go through with our plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.19,1:13:11.06,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,飞雪问我 为何不杀秦王?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.46,1:13:13.89,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I told her the King of Qin must not be killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.46,1:13:13.89,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我告诉她 秦王不能杀
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.53,1:13:17.33,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,This was something I had come to realize through studying calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.53,1:13:17.33,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,这是我从书法的境界中悟出的道理
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.90,1:13:20.03,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Because I spared the king,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.90,1:13:20.03,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我没有杀秦王
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.90,1:13:22.63,英文字幕,,0,0,0,, Snow turned her back on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.90,1:13:22.63,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,飞雪从此不再理我
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.14,1:13:30.30,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Please abort your plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.14,1:13:30.30,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,请你放弃
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.81,1:13:31.61,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.81,1:13:31.61,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.98,1:13:34.01,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Was all your training motivated by hatred and revenge?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.98,1:13:34.01,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你的剑莫非只为仇恨而练?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.65,1:13:35.55,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.65,1:13:35.55,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.59,1:13:37.48,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,For 10 years, I worked relentlessly
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.59,1:13:37.48,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我的剑
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.02,1:13:41.45,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,without a moment's rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.02,1:13:41.45,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,十年来不敢有一刻倦怠
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.89,1:13:43.08,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What will it take to dissuade you?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.89,1:13:43.08,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你如何才肯听?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.79,1:13:45.09,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You will have to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.79,1:13:45.09,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,除非你杀了我
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.93,1:13:46.99,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,So you are determined to go ahead?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.93,1:13:46.99,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你一定要去?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.76,1:13:48.56,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.76,1:13:48.56,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.63,1:13:52.10,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,In that case
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.63,1:13:52.10,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,那好
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.00,1:13:54.63,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I shall make you a gift of two words.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.00,1:13:54.63,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我送你两个字
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.51,1:14:32.71,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,These words reflect what is in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.51,1:14:32.71,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,字同我心
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.08,1:14:35.21,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Please think again.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.08,1:14:35.21,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,望你三思
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.46,1:14:47.45,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Moon, give my sword to the nameless hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.46,1:14:47.45,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如月 把剑交给无名大侠
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.06,1:14:49.62,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Just as Snow and I will always be together,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.06,1:14:49.62,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我跟飞雪人不离人
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.97,1:14:51.06,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,our swords will never be apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.97,1:14:51.06,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,剑不离剑
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.92,1:15:07.08,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Master Nameless,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.92,1:15:07.08,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,无名大侠
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.08,1:15:09.64,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,even though I am only a lowly servant,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.08,1:15:09.64,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如月虽身份卑微
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.25,1:15:11.72,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,please permit me a few words.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.25,1:15:11.72,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,也愿为主人一劝
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.99,1:15:16.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I have served my master since I was eight.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.99,1:15:16.20,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如月身为丫环 八岁跟了主人
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.96,1:15:20.00,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,MFrom him I learnt the martial arts and how to live with principles.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.96,1:15:20.00,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,随主人研习武艺 更懂得做人的道理
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.66,1:15:23.00,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,My master is
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.66,1:15:23.00,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,主人做的事
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.30,1:15:24.63,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,never wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.30,1:15:24.63,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,一定不会错
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.00,1:15:27.33,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What he wrote
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.00,1:15:27.33,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,主人给你写的字
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.80,1:15:29.03,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,must be important.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.80,1:15:29.03,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,一定有道理
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.35,1:15:30.65,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Master Nameless,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.35,1:15:30.65,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,无名大侠
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.18,1:15:32.62,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,please consider his advice carefully.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.18,1:15:32.62,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.34,1:15:49.83,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Which two words did Broken Sword write?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.34,1:15:49.83,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,残剑给你写了哪两个字?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.11,1:15:51.07,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,"Our Land."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.11,1:15:51.07,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,天下
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.78,1:15:53.57,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,"Our Land."
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.78,1:15:53.57,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,天下
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.78,1:15:54.64,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Broken Sword said
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.78,1:15:54.64,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,残剑说
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.15,1:15:58.90,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,for years there has been continuous warfare, causing huge suffering to the people.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.15,1:15:58.90,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,七国连年混战 百姓受苦
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.05,1:16:01.28,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Only your majesty has the power
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.05,1:16:01.28,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,唯有大王才能停止战乱
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.99,1:16:03.21,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,to bring peace by uniting our land.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.99,1:16:03.21,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,一统天下
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.16,1:16:07.62,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,He hoped that for the sake of the greater good,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.16,1:16:07.62,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,残剑希望我 为了天下
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.04,1:16:10.37,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I would abandon my plan to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.04,1:16:10.37,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,放弃刺杀大王
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.76,1:16:13.56,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Broken Sword also said, "One person's pain is nothing...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.76,1:16:13.56,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,他跟我说 一个人的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.76,1:16:17.88,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,... when compared to the suffering of all."
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.76,1:16:17.88,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,与天下人比 便不再是痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.07,1:16:19.80,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The conflict between Zhao and Qin...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.07,1:16:19.80,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,赵国与秦国的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.30,1:16:23.60,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,is nothing when compared with peace for all.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.30,1:16:23.60,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,放到天下 也不再是仇恨
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.25,1:16:30.21,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Who would have thought an assassin
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.25,1:16:30.21,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,没想到最了解寡人的
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.41,1:16:33.14,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,would understand me the best!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.41,1:16:33.14,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,竟是寡人通缉的刺客
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.59,1:16:40.32,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Alone in my position I have endured endless criticism,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.59,1:16:40.32,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.52,1:16:44.19,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,endless attempts on my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.52,1:16:44.19,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,忍受多少责难 多少暗算
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.39,1:16:46.69,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,No one has ever grasped what I have been trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.39,1:16:46.69,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,无人能懂寡人之心
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.13,1:16:49.43,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Even my own court
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.13,1:16:49.43,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,就连秦国的满朝文武
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.87,1:16:53.13,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,regards me as a tyrant.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.87,1:16:53.13,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,也视寡人为暴君
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.77,1:16:58.67,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,And yet, Broken Sword,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.77,1:16:58.67,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,想不到残剑
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.88,1:17:01.00,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,a man I barely knew,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.88,1:17:01.00,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,与寡人素昧平生
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.21,1:17:03.48,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,was able to see clearly,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.21,1:17:03.48,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,才真正懂得寡人
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.02,1:17:08.25,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,what is truly in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.02,1:17:08.25,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,与寡人心意相通
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.00,1:17:21.86,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I want to know,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.00,1:17:21.86,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人想知道
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.10,1:17:25.19,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,without a sword, how do you intend to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.10,1:17:25.19,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你手无寸铁 如何刺我?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.94,1:17:26.96,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,By taking yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.94,1:17:26.96,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,夺剑
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.95,1:17:42.89,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,For 10 years this sword
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.95,1:17:42.89,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,此剑随寡人征战南北
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.09,1:17:44.61,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,has accompanied me to every battle.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.09,1:17:44.61,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,也有十年了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.39,1:17:48.48,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,To have been understood by a man such as Broken Sword...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.39,1:17:48.48,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人能有残剑大侠这样的知己
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.69,1:17:51.42,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,allows me to face death without fear or regret.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.69,1:17:51.42,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,便是死 也足矣
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.30,1:17:54.82,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Let the good of our country...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.30,1:17:54.82,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你就为天下
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.43,1:17:58.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,guide your decision!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.43,1:17:58.20,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,决定这一剑吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.13,1:19:55.53,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I have just come to a realization!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.13,1:19:55.53,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,寡人悟到了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.26,1:19:57.42,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,This scroll by Broken Sword contains
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.26,1:19:57.42,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,残剑的这幅字
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.63,1:19:59.66,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,no secrets of his swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.63,1:19:59.66,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,根本就不含剑法招式
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.87,1:20:02.39,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What this reveals is his highest ideal.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.87,1:20:02.39,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,写的是剑法的最高境界
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.90,1:20:05.70,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,In the first stage,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.90,1:20:05.70,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,剑法 其第一层境界
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.07,1:20:07.44,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,man and sword become
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.07,1:20:07.44,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,讲求人剑合一
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.64,1:20:09.70,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,one and each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.64,1:20:09.70,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,剑就是人 人就是剑
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.91,1:20:12.04,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Here, even a blade of grass can be used as a lethal weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.91,1:20:12.04,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,手中寸草 也是利器
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.68,1:20:14.17,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,In the next stage,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.68,1:20:14.17,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,其第二层境界
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.68,1:20:17.88,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,the sword resides not in the hand, but in the heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.68,1:20:17.88,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,讲求手中无剑 剑在心中
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.09,1:20:20.49,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Even without a weapon,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.09,1:20:20.49,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,虽赤手空拳 却能以剑气
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.69,1:20:23.02,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,the warrior can slay his enemy from 100 paces.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.69,1:20:23.02,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,杀敌于百步之外
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.72,1:20:25.66,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,But the ultimate ideal is...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.72,1:20:25.66,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,而剑法的最高境界
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.43,1:20:30.12,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,when the sword disappears altogether.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.43,1:20:30.12,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,则是手中无剑 心中也无剑
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.43,1:20:31.66,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The warrior embraces
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.43,1:20:31.66,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是以大胸怀
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.87,1:20:33.06,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,all around him.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.87,1:20:33.06,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,包容一切
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.67,1:20:36.19,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,The desire to kill no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.67,1:20:36.19,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,那便是不杀
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.97,1:20:38.44,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Only peace remains.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.97,1:20:38.44,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,便是和平
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.23,1:21:09.33,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, I have now completed my mission.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.23,1:21:09.33,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,大王 这一剑臣必须刺
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.54,1:21:13.87,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Because of my decision today,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.54,1:21:13.87,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,刺了这一剑
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.84,1:21:16.21,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,many will die,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.84,1:21:16.21,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,很多人都会死
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.21,1:21:19.61,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,and your majesty will go on living.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.21,1:21:19.61,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,而大王会活着
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.88,1:21:25.88,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,A dead man  begs you never to forget...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.88,1:21:25.88,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,死去的人请大王记住
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.12,1:21:29.11,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,the ultimate ideal for a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.12,1:21:29.11,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,那最高的境界
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.91,1:23:32.81,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Nameless came within 10 paces of the king.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.91,1:23:32.81,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,无名已近秦王十步
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.02,1:23:36.42,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,He could not have failed.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.02,1:23:36.42,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,他的剑是不会失手的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.69,1:23:39.85,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,There can be only one explanation.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.69,1:23:39.85,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 只有一个解释
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.26,1:23:41.88,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,He must have given up willingly.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.26,1:23:41.88,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,是他自己愿意放弃
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.53,1:23:45.50,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,What did you say to him?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.53,1:23:45.50,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你到底跟他说了什么?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.96,1:23:47.45,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I wrote two words.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.96,1:23:47.45,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我只写了两个字
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.20,1:23:49.17,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Which two words?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.20,1:23:49.17,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,哪两个字?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.17,1:23:51.19,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,"Our Land."
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.17,1:23:51.19,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,天下
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.60,1:23:56.20,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Is that all there is in your heart?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.60,1:23:56.20,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你心里只有天下
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.44,1:23:57.13,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,There is also you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.44,1:23:57.13,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,还有你
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.41,1:24:00.27,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I don't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.41,1:24:00.27,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我不信
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.74,1:24:01.87,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,How can I convince you?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.74,1:24:01.87,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,如何让你信?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.65,1:24:11.48,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Draw your sword!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.65,1:24:11.48,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,拔剑
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.22,1:24:15.32,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,You have killed Nameless,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.22,1:24:15.32,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你害了无名
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.93,1:24:18.36,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,betrayed Sky, and destroyed Zhao.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.93,1:24:18.36,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,害了长空 害了赵国
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.80,1:24:19.63,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Draw your sword!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.80,1:24:19.63,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,拔剑
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.77,1:24:25.43,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,When we first met,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.77,1:24:25.43,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,当初我们相识的时候
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.57,1:24:28.87,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,you asked me to draw my sword then.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.57,1:24:28.87,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你也要我拔剑
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.28,1:24:33.47,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Is the sword the only answer?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.28,1:24:33.47,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你如何才信?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.24,1:24:35.64,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I just want you to draw your sword.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.24,1:24:35.64,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我只要你拔剑
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.30,1:26:00.93,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Why did you not defend yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.30,1:26:00.93,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你为什么不挡我的剑?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.34,1:26:03.67,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,So you would finally believe me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.34,1:26:03.67,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,这样你就信了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.01,1:26:13.98,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,I have always wanted to go home with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.01,1:26:13.98,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,我一直都想跟你回家
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.62,1:26:20.95,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,That will not happen now.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.62,1:26:20.95,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,可惜不能去了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.29,1:26:27.92,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,On your own, you must take good care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.29,1:26:27.92,中文字幕,,0,0,0,,你一个人好好保重
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.88,1:26:43.67,英文字幕,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you block my sword?
